_json.description: The fabulously versatile St Edmund's pendant with it's softly rounded enamel dish shade brings style to both traditional and contemporary settings. With a wide, downwards projection of light this pendant is perfect for task lighting whilst aesthetically enhancing any interior. The hand painted soft green finish is a soothingly refined colour and is paired with a choice of bulb holder including gold, black nickel, chrome, brass, copper and nickel.
